      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\"><style>[data-colorid=w4or2pjnms]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=w4or2pjnms]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=tm6cgrydi1]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=tm6cgrydi1]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=xuvnkfhulc]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=xuvnkfhulc]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=h5quct3bf6]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=h5quct3bf6]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=ypjjvi1wt1]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=ypjjvi1wt1]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=jwfoq0ae78]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=jwfoq0ae78]{color:#004eb3}</style>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"challengeHeader.png\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/573505543/challengeHeader.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1756475680794&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=373\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/573505543/challengeHeader.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1756475680794&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"606\" data-width=\"1232\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"578224160\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"challengeHeader.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"573505543\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"25\" data-media-id=\"406c63f2-e890-46e6-9201-e73b72577bd5\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/573505543/challengeHeader.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1756475680794&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1232&amp;height=606 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/573505543/challengeHeader.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1756475680794&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=373 1x\" /></span><h1 id=\"RenderManArtChallenge-RenderManArtChallengeHelpGuide\"><span data-colorid=\"ypjjvi1wt1\">RenderMan Art Challenge Help Guide </span></h1><p>The RenderMan Art Challenge is an exciting yearly opportunity for creatives around the world to showcase their talents using Pixar&rsquo;s RenderMan ... for a chance to win amazing prizes!</p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://renderman.pixar.com/challenges\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"learn-more-docs-button.png\" width=\"196\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/573505543/learn-more-docs-button.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1759278980037&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=196&amp;height=46\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/573505543/learn-more-docs-button.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1759278980037&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"68\" data-width=\"286\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"616726564\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"learn-more-docs-button.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"573505543\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"25\" data-media-id=\"fa0c5022-055b-494e-a0a0-8b5231f8f87a\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/573505543/learn-more-docs-button.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1759278980037&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=286&amp;height=68 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/573505543/learn-more-docs-button.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1759278980037&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=196&amp;height=46 1x\" /></span></a><p>These pages will help you not only plan your time and gather references, but also spark ideas to make your creative journey a success.</p><hr /><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-right-sidebar\" data-layout=\"two-right-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/569278526/Idea+Seeds\" data-linked-resource-id=\"569278526\" data-linked-resource-version=\"30\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"ideasseeds12.jpg\" width=\"586\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/573505543/ideasseeds12.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1756479623409&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/573505543/ideasseeds12.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1756479623409&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"255\" data-width=\"586\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"578387995\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"ideasseeds12.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"573505543\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"25\" data-media-id=\"4683f254-fcf3-4b5a-9631-d130d7650784\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/573505543/ideasseeds12.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1756479623409&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/573505543/ideasseeds12.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1756479623409&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 1x\" /></span></a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell aside\" data-type=\"aside\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h1 id=\"RenderManArtChallenge-IdeaSeeds\"><span data-colorid=\"h5quct3bf6\">Idea Seeds</span></h1><p>Need ideas?</p><p>Here&rsquo;s a good place to start!</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-right-sidebar\" data-layout=\"two-right-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/RU/568787000\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"words.jpg\" width=\"586\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/573505543/words.jpg?version=5&amp;modificationDate=1757333839060&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/573505543/words.jpg?version=5&amp;modificationDate=1757333839060&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"255\" data-width=\"586\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"578387988\" data-linked-resource-version=\"5\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"words.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"573505543\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"25\" data-media-id=\"83d79561-2931-40b9-83c6-e12136a443ea\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/573505543/words.jpg?version=5&amp;modificationDate=1757333839060&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/573505543/words.jpg?version=5&amp;modificationDate=1757333839060&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 1x\" /></span></a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell aside\" data-type=\"aside\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h1 id=\"RenderManArtChallenge-StartwithWords\"><span data-colorid=\"jwfoq0ae78\">Start with Words</span></h1><p>Now that you have your amazing idea, start writing it up and developing it further.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-right-sidebar\" data-layout=\"two-right-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/568557622/Adding+Wonder\" data-linked-resource-id=\"568557622\" data-linked-resource-version=\"7\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"addwonder.jpg\" width=\"586\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/573505543/addwonder.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1756637391323&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/573505543/addwonder.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1756637391323&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"255\" data-width=\"586\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"579534926\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"addwonder.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-reso