ki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"573505543\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"25\" data-media-id=\"d628740c-6fd0-4ecf-92e6-a5507b718528\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/573505543/STRONGIMAGE.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1756826502466&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/573505543/STRONGIMAGE.jpg?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1756826502466&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 1x\" /></span></a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell aside\" data-type=\"aside\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h1 id=\"RenderManArtChallenge-Whatmakesastrongimage?\"><span data-colorid=\"w4or2pjnms\">What makes a strong image?</span></h1><p>A few thoughts from industry professionals on what elements make for a strong image.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-right-sidebar\" data-layout=\"two-right-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/622592143/Mentoring+Session+Archive\" data-linked-resource-id=\"622592143\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"mentoring_banner.jpg\" width=\"565\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/573505543/mentoring_banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1760016177025&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=565&amp;height=238\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/573505543/mentoring_banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1760016177025&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"238\" data-width=\"565\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-i